h — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8514,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Deep Research: Spec Kit Memory Feature Audit & Quality [system-spec-kit/023-hybrid-rag-fusion-refinement/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6864,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/048-system-analysis\",\n          \"title\": \"048: SpecKit & Memory [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/048-system-analysis/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"remediation\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6831,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec Kit [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/042-post-merge-refinement-5/decision-record]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"memory\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6678,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/019-speckit-refinement\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Specification: SpecKit Refinement: ECP Analysis & Improvements\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"refinement\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"implementation\",\n            \"verification\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T04:41:14.669Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 2174\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781757672486,"end":1781757674692}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0fb794cc4554a129016a3376e513d481919198febbcc95c355"}},"id":"prt_ed9086eee001rYc9wRjaM4xdKA","sessionID":"ses_126f83aa4ffekBSRvWmpN9g5Xg","messageID":"msg_ed90857f3001pNBEMIdptFHmDc"}}
