 finding directly contradicts the shipped starter-set loader path.\",\"results\":[{\"protocolId\":\"spec_code\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"gateClass\":\"hard\",\"applicable\":true,\"counts\":{\"pass\":1,\"partial\":1,\"fail\":0,\"skipped\":0},\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/spec.md:78-79\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/confidence-calibration.ts:73-76\"],\"findingRefs\":[\"F001\"],\"summary\":\"Calibration default-off wiring and rebalance are present; starter labeled-set loading is only partial due the JSON shape mismatch.\"},{\"protocolId\":\"checklist_evidence\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"gateClass\":\"hard\",\"applicable\":true,\"counts\":{\"pass\":0,\"partial\":1,\"fail\":0,\"skipped\":0},\"evidence\":[\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/tasks.md:65-78\"],\"findingRefs\":[],\"summary\":\"Checked task rows exist, but this lineage did not run validation commands due the write restriction and one-iteration budget.\"}]},\"newFindingsRatio\":1,\"semanticNovelty\":1,\"findingStability\":0,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.5-fast\",\"lineage\":\"gpt55-p017c004-2\"},\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-18T04:45:00Z\"}\n+{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"claim_adjudication\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"run\":1,\"passed\":true,\"packets\":[{\"findingId\":\"F001\",\"claim\":\"The bundled starter labeled-set artifact cannot be accepted by the shipped loadLabeledSet() API because the loader requires a top-level array while the generator and artifact emit an object containing pairs.\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/confidence-calibration.ts:73-76\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-r